<m0>Democrats' dilemma: What <m2><ql>
<ql>
hat <m0>to do about Barakat?<ql>
<m1><ue5><m2><ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.76 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.041 INCHES<m2><ql>
